title: v0.5.0
description:
partial re-write of Strut.

Concrete goals:
* Responsive design
* Support Impress/Jimpress/Reveal/ other backends
* Seamless integration of online and local storage
* UI improvements and simplifications as outlined in issues: #64 #73 #69 #64 #57 #44 and others

Purpose: 
* Clean up the code base
* Re-define the models as Strut has grown, and will continue to grow, to be more that initially intended
* Move logic out of views that belong in models (this is a part of the above task)
